{"tid":507038,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"龍的傳人 做冬　黃河流域吃餃子　長江流域各不同　糯米飯 湯果 擂圓 冬釀酒 麻糍","createTime":"2017-12-22T20:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T08:16:10.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"39f1209522ba13d6edc5003033e07f0d6b4a19f1","tid":507038,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T20:05:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/冬至\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh%2F%E5%86%AC%E8%87%B3&d=Rq0KpPxW9tA6I4%2Fq6ambdbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=ed5efe8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/冬至</a><br />\n<br />\n有諺語「冬至餃子夏至麵」，認為冬天寒冷而人體耗熱量多故應該多吃有營養的食品補充熱量。因此有冬至日有吃餃子和餛飩的習俗：吃餛飩寓意破陰釋陽，表達冬至的新舊交接宇宙混沌狀態，更意味親自開闢世界；而吃餃子又俗稱「安耳朵」（擠餃形似耳朵），民間習俗認為冬至日不吃餃子會凍掉耳朵，也不利農事收穫；另一說吃餃子防為紀念藥王張仲景。而餃子、餛飩和包子等更會是家庭成員團聚圍桌而食，稱為「蒸冬」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=ca4b3d068d1001e94a3c130d880f7b06/9d82d158ccbf6c81e98d5807bc3eb13532fa40a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss1.bdstatic.com%2F9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy%2Fbaike%2Fs%253D220%2Fsign%3Dca4b3d068d1001e94a3c130d880f7b06%2F9d82d158ccbf6c81e98d5807bc3eb13532fa40a2.jpg&h=55acd2b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/item/冬至/9381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbaike.baidu.com%2Fitem%2F%E5%86%AC%E8%87%B3%2F9381&d=Rq0KpPxW9tA6I4%2Fq6ambdbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=1322142d\" target=\"_blank\">http://baike.baidu.com/item/冬至/9381</a><br />\n<br />\n江南米飯<br />\n<br />\n在江南水鄉，有冬至之夜全家歡聚一堂共吃赤豆糯米飯的習俗。<br />\n相傳，共工氏有不才子，作惡多端，死於冬至這一天，死後變成疫鬼，繼續殘害百姓。但是，這個疫鬼最怕赤豆，於是，人們就在冬至這一天煮吃赤豆飯，用以驅避疫鬼，防災祛病。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=13acfdee5c6034a82de2bf83fb1249d9/b812c8fcc3cec3fd768ad39ad688d43f869427ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss2.bdstatic.com%2F9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy%2Fbaike%2Fs%253D220%2Fsign%3D13acfdee5c6034a82de2bf83fb1249d9%2Fb812c8fcc3cec3fd768ad39ad688d43f869427ac.jpg&h=b2e3b5ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n番薯湯果<br />\n<br />\n在寧波的傳統習俗中，番薯湯果是冬至必吃的美食之一。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=9fc44283f103738dda4a0b20831ab073/279759ee3d6d55fb943e4b056a224f4a20a4dd1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss2.bdstatic.com%2F-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy%2Fbaike%2Fs%253D220%2Fsign%3D9fc44283f103738dda4a0b20831ab073%2F279759ee3d6d55fb943e4b056a224f4a20a4dd1c.jpg&h=2995ed97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浙江台州擂圓<br />\n<br />\n浙江台州人好美食，冬至是一年中重要節氣，在這一天要做些特色菜餚和食物，首先要祭奠祖先，祈禱祖先保佑全家人來年一切平安如意。然後全家人歡樂地聚在一起喝酒吃菜。其中吃&ldquo;冬至圓&rdquo;（擂圓，又叫硬擂圓、翻糙圓）是台州的老傳統，擂圓取圓圓潤潤、團圓之意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gss3.bdstatic.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=2e6287194dc2d562f608d7efd71090f3/a9d3fd1f4134970aa714395697cad1c8a7865d67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss3.bdstatic.com%2F7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy%2Fbaike%2Fs%253D220%2Fsign%3D2e6287194dc2d562f608d7efd71090f3%2Fa9d3fd1f4134970aa714395697cad1c8a7865d67.jpg&h=d96747ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江西麻糍<br />\n<br />\n麻糍，是浙江，江西的特產，也是福建人的傳統小吃、福建人祭祀時的供品。麻糍陰乾後蒸、煎、火烤、砂炒皆宜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gss3.bdstatic.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/w%3D268%3Bg%3D0/sign=3a4e59486e061d957d46303e43cf6dec/d009b3de9c82d1585ff079c1800a19d8bc3e424b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss3.bdstatic.com%2F-Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy%2Fbaike%2Fw%253D268%253Bg%253D0%2Fsign%3D3a4e59486e061d957d46303e43cf6dec%2Fd009b3de9c82d1585ff079c1800a19d8bc3e424b.jpg&h=1bf668ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n安徽合肥吃冬至麵<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;吃了冬至麵，一天長一線&rdquo;。在安徽合肥，冬至吃麵的風俗與節氣、氣候、農事有關。冬至過後即是數九寒天，每隔九天數作一九。在滴水成冰的嚴冬，吃一碗熱騰騰的雞蛋掛麵，才算是過了一個冬至。<br />\n<br />\n合肥南瓜餅<br />\n<br />\n冬至過了眼看年，合肥人到了冬至都要吃南瓜餅，大街小巷瀰漫著南瓜餅的香味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=8b9657708cd4b31cf43c93b9b7d6276f/9922720e0cf3d7cabab07345f51fbe096b63a9bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss1.bdstatic.com%2F9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy%2Fbaike%2Fs%253D220%2Fsign%3D8b9657708cd4b31cf43c93b9b7d6276f%2F9922720e0cf3d7cabab07345f51fbe096b63a9bb.jpg&h=6875c110&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e484caa268e362770d3de1f46957f9fca6905b9","tid":507038,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T07:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2fa7b758863f2edcd1a65f8c8a0ec1deff87ce","tid":507038,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T07:46:54.000Z","msg":"珠江流域呢？"},{"pid":"9986e2b39d8171aa396023c552cb8821d6100e12","tid":507038,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de2fa7b758863f2edcd1a65f8c8a0ec1deff87ce","tid":507038,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T07:46:54.000Z","msg":"珠江流域呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T08:08:24.000Z","msg":"都話龍的傳人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b37d920510abc3f491cc6bb71e6ef2dedc379c","tid":507038,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T08:16:10.000Z","msg":"中國人係龍的傳人呢個講法只係有幾拾年"}]}